---
title: Sirloin Steak, Smoky Wedges & Chorizo Salsa with a Rocket and Tomato Salad
description: We love a good Sirloin Steak with Wedges, Salad & Salsa and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
